  %h2.article-title Private & shared mixins
  The above example describes shared mixins.  If you need to automate 
  some calculations inside specific <strong>module</strong> create 
  private mixin right in the begining of the current module file:

  %pre<
    %code<
      :preserve
        // scrollbox.sass
        
        =center-slider($size)
          height: $size
          margin-left: -($size / 2)
          right: -($size / 2)
          width: $size

